
//How To run
1. cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/w/halla-scifs17exp/sbs/thir/libsbsdig-install ../ && make install
2. sbsdig db_gmn_conf.dat gmn13.5_elastic_ex.txt 100000

//Add a new detector (POLSCINT_BS)
1. Add a new detector on the line 6 of db_gmn_conf.dat
2. Add digitization parameters in it
3. Add those parameters into sbsdig.cxx
4. Copy the block line 231-242, and change the variables names like in the database (Copy paste and define the type right)
5. Add and change following:
  if(skey=="sigmapulse_POLSCINT_BS"){  // => the name here should be compatible with the name listed on the database
             TString stemp = ( (TObjString*) (*tokens)[1] )->GetString();
                    sigmapulse_POLSCINT_BS = stemp.Atof();//the name here should be compatible with the name defined earlier in sbsdig.cxx
                         }
6. Declare detectors: Add PRPOLSCINT_BS at the end or replaced BBHODO by PRPOLSCINT_BS
                      bbhodo=>prpolscint_bs from there, it should add the detector in the list of detectors and try to process it
7. If it goes through, then go to:
    src/SBSDigAuxi.cxx
8. Now, go to
   src/SBSDigPMTSignal.cxx
   lines 448-482 copy, and change "Earm_BBHodo_Dig" to "Harm_PRPolScintBeamSide_Dig"
   oh, and don't forget to change (both there and in what you did in SBSDigAuxi.cxx)
    HODO_UNIQUE_DETID with PRPOLBS_SCINT_UNIQUE_DETID
9. Harm_PRPolScintBeamSide and Harm_PRPolScintBeamSide_Dig are defined in
    src/g4sbs_tree.h lines 173, 174
